<plot>A year after her boyfriend committed suicide and her mother passed away, Cary Meadows has moved into her new home in a quiet neighborhood. After meeting Keith, Cary's life changes as she finds she has feelings which she thought were forever forgotten. As their relationship grows, Cary and Keith unbox an antique radio from her mother's attic, only to discover that holding on to the item holds dire consequences.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?067523</url></doc>
